{"tid":2235365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡錫進瘋了：這個謠言太坑人了，今天有好幾個人管我借錢……","createTime":"2020-10-08T15:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T17:16:39.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9aa9b6ce4a1fbeb66c059ab4ae78e24e700208","tid":2235365,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">胡錫進</span></strong><br />\n46分鐘前 來自 HUAWEI P30 Pro<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">這個謠言太坑人了，今天有好幾個人管我借錢&hellip;&hellip;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n@胡錫進<br />\n<span class=\"red\">之前有自媒體造謠說，老胡一年收入1200萬元以上。因為它太離奇，一看就是假的，我未予回應。</span>不曾想，7日蘋果日報通過與海外不嚴肅網站&ldquo;接龍&rdquo;，接過了這個謠言，並且把老胡&ldquo;在加拿大有個兒子&rdquo;的謠言一起重炒一遍。蘋果日報這樣幹太不專業也太沒底線了吧，他們的記者可以打個電話向我求證啊（他們之前為別的事聯繫過我），為何要把這個很明顯的謠言當可靠信息加以報導放大呢？蘋果日報的消息不會都是按照這樣質量標準生產出來的吧？<br />\n<br />\n最近針對老胡的謠言越來越多，我知道，有一些力量恨我，想要用誹謗壓垮我。對陷入這樣的處境，<span class=\"red\">我不抱怨，這大概是我獲得影響力並且將它用於捍衛國家利益必須承受的代價</span>。但我想說，那些力量壓不垮我，哈哈，我說過很多次了：老胡奄奄一息地活著並且長壽。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以通過老胡的遭遇看清當下的輿論場上有多少明槍暗箭，以及它們的背後又有多少狡詐和無情。至於老胡本人，<span class=\"red\">我常對自己說：出來混，就要堅強些，心大些。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDSsG0z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDSsG0z.png&h=b62299fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQx4KdZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQx4KdZ.png&h=6a5b47d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZAmMsn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZAmMsn.png&h=d4f4563a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc53132ba24edb98b05ca7fd47c8b2568633bf6d","tid":2235365,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MemMXzf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMemMXzf.png&h=bf574de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFFuaUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFFuaUi.png&h=0cf3fdaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fc7oZNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffc7oZNG.png&h=d7a6765c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b83aeb5d42550481120705bbc629bac66f3d753c","tid":2235365,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8jrc8O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8jrc8O.png&h=2345aba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RxXjOR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RxXjOR.png&h=daf51df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bbEx8U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bbEx8U.png&h=673ee434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32dce976dd562e1be9b919819707f03a78afa2f7","tid":2235365,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2020/0706/20200706104231465.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2020%2F0706%2F20200706104231465.jpg&h=dd7ecdc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"591ce776d80689a64b850833369e8578e9195c9c","tid":2235365,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"唔譴責？唔澄明？唔告蘋果誹謗？唔出律師信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad55b518c4d4da9a39c315ad8da21f1ddbda3043","tid":2235365,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591ce776d80689a64b850833369e8578e9195c9c","tid":2235365,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08